        <mxCell id="n8_2" value="[操作回退]&#xa;**删除增程商品**&#xa;登录CAC → 执行 delete 脚本&#xa;参数：service/delete/obsBillExtendProduct/DomainId=${DomainId}&#xa;填写DomainId/ProductName → 提交任务" style="rounded=10;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF3E0;strokeColor=#FFB74D;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="container">
